title: The sexiest spots in Australia revealed
text:
What are these? Where are the nation’s highest libidos? Source: Supplied 
AUSSIES, if you’re finding your sex drive is dwindling, it turns out that you may be in the wrong spot. 
Dating site EliteSingles.com.au quizzed 25,000 single Australians to see who has the highest and lowest libidos around the nation. 
And according to their study, there may be something in the water, with those in beachside destinations such as the Sydney suburbs of Coogee, Manly, Cronulla and Bondi reporting some of the strongest sex drives. 
There were some notable places missing from the list: Western Australia, South Australia, Tasmania and the Northern Territory didn’t rate a mention! 
And of course we can’t all be winners; the survey also revealed the locations of the smallest libidos. Victoria, we feel for you. 
Top 10 places with the highest libidos:

2. Manly, NSW
